{
  "stem": "3659.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were two or three SS men standing there with guns drawn and said, where's the Jew?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where are all the Jews?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother said my father isn't here, and they came in to look.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't find my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the meantime, two other men rounded up all the people that lived in our building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before we knew it, they herded all the people into our apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And most of the people that lived in our building were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think there was only one or two families that weren't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody said, try to get the consulate, because-- the consul general-- because his mother was also pushed into our apartment.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, they ransacked all the apartments in the-- in the building of the other people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they locked-- oh, we were there maybe 22 people, 24 people in our home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they locked the doors and they said, we'll get to you guys later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are they going to burn us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Are they going to annihilate us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What are they going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother said, you know, double clothing, triple clothing, get prepared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know what they're going to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Took eight hours.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Finally, they found the consul general, and somehow he pulled strings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, you're on foreign territory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You must leave this building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he had to get his mother out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I would say maybe the whole thing lasted for about 12, 14 hours until everybody was able to go back to-- in the meantime, people were hysterical because we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are they going to burn us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was one lady that totally couldn't [? endure ?] and she kept saying, they're coming with the torches.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
